scene.message:
Mark: You idiot...{nl}
That's why I said you{nl}
couldn't take him alone.{wait_fr:88} He's gone now.{waitkey}He went off to our world.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
What are you doing...{nl}
Hurry up and chase him!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: But how...{nl}
We have no way{nl}
to get back!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: No way!{nl}
There's no beating a guy{nl}
with something like that?{waitkey}And how would we even{nl}
get back, huh?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: How do we get back?!{nl}
Call a chauffeur or somethin'?{nl}
And even if we did...{waitkey}{clearbox}There's nothing we can do{nl}
about that guy!{nl}
It's all over...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}There's got{nl}
to be some way...{nl}
That's the kind of guy he is.{waitkey}{clearbox}He's toying with us{nl}
and enjoying it...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kido's right.{nl}
There's always a way...{nl}
Heh. First time we've agreed.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...Maybe it's there.{nl}
That place with the old{nl}
rumors of spirited-aways.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: The haunted manor!{nl}
I used to sneak in as a kid{nl}
and get my butt smacked{nl}
by my mom...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It overlaps with{nl}
SEBEC in our world...{nl}
There's a chance.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's impossible!{nl}
We have no proof at all!{waitkey}{clearbox}And how are we to fight{nl}
an opponent with such...{nl}
with such power?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: No way!{nl}
No matter how hard you try,{nl}
what's no good is no good!{waitkey}It's always been that way{nl}
up till now...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No way!{nl}
Why? Why does this{nl}
have to happen to Ayase?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: We can't give up!{nl}
It's everyone's world,{nl}
everyone's future, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is it okay to let others{nl}
do as they please?{nl}
To just throw it away?{nl}
I can't stand that!{waitkey}{clearbox}I love this town!{nl}
I love everyone!{nl}
I love myself!{waitkey}{clearbox}I won't sit silent while{nl}
the things I love are{nl}
destroyed! That's just{nl}
not who I am!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{wait_fr:108}You're right.{nl}
Standing here gets us nowhere.{nl}
Let's go.{waitkey}To protect the people{nl}
who matter to us!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: ...{wait_fr:79}All right!{nl}
The leader is reborn!{waitkey}The tougher the villain,{nl}
the more the hero shines!{nl}
Let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...{wait_fr:79}Well, fine.{nl}
Ayase's future's on{nl}
the line too, after all.{waitkey}Let's go! The haunted manor!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Things you love, huh...{nl}
Guess nobody's complaining.{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, let's go{nl}
to the haunted manor!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Damn!{nl}
We wasted some dumb time.{waitkey}If we don't catch that{nl}
bastard fast, things'll{nl}
get out of hand!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}There's got{nl}
to be some way...{nl}
That's the kind of guy he is.{waitkey}{clearbox}He's toying with us{nl}
and enjoying it...{waitkey}I won't give up!{nl}
Not till I kill him{nl}
with these hands.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonomura...{nl}
From here on, it's a problem{nl}
for our world.{waitkey}It's okay now. Go home.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No!{nl}
Just watching from the{nl}
sidelines - I can't bear it!{waitkey}{clearbox}I love this town!{nl}
I love everyone!{nl}
I love myself!{waitkey}{clearbox}I won't sit silent while{nl}
the things I love are{nl}
destroyed! That's just{nl}
not who I am!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Heh...{nl}
'In youth's dictionary,{nl}
there's no word for failure.'{waitkey}A naive old saying, but{nl}
shall we believe it?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}Get moving!{nl}
I'll look after{nl}
my own damn self!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: To think that compact{nl}
could make something{nl}
like that...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Kido,{nl}
we'll come back for you,{nl}
so don't you worry.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Tch!{nl}
That was nothing.{nl}
Like I'd kick it before you.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Heh...{wait_fr:60} Not bad.{nl}
Don't you forget{nl}
those words.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
that Reiji's finally{nl}
talking like a normal guy.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We mustn't give in{nl}
to weakness so easily,{nl}
must we.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Can't go around{nl}
with our tails tucked{nl}
forever, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yeah, true.{waitkey}If we do nothing,{nl}
Ayase's future boyfriend{nl}
dies too, right?{waitkey}{ret}
